321
00:13:06,095 --> 00:13:07,974
Right, you're just in time.

322
00:13:07,975 --> 00:13:09,535
Let's all put our cards on the table.

323
00:13:09,536 --> 00:13:11,155
Xiang Zhijun, ask her.

324
00:13:11,296 --> 00:13:12,356
Deng Haiyang

325
