363
00:14:08,136 --> 00:14:08,734
Okay?

364
00:14:08,735 --> 00:14:09,775
Shut up!

365
00:14:09,776 --> 00:14:10,875
Stop talking!

366
00:14:12,296 --> 00:14:15,476
